{"tid":684204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土豪終抱得女神歸！新娘：不愛黃金只愛你！","createTime":"2018-05-30T10:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T12:25:59.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a2451712ec0d898b1d18c77b2c653e0a613e7100","tid":684204,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"土豪表達愛意靠掛上一堆金手鐲？<br />\n中國陶瓷大亨黃英明獨子上年識咗貌美如花嘅珠海女神，他們一見鍾情，在今年3月仲結埋婚。婚禮當日，男方為咗證明自己的愛，特別幫新娘子掛上一堆金手鐲、金項鍊同5克拉鑽戒。<br />\n<br />\n號稱世紀婚姻！<br />\n這場可以說是世紀婚姻，除了場地門外放滿跑車名車，仲請了不同女子團體同偶像歌手勁歌熱舞，令到在場嘅人都呆了。<br />\n<br />\n「不愛黃金只愛你。」<br />\n不要以為這位新娘係是為了錢，佢在婚禮上同現場親友講，她不在乎丈夫黃金有幾兩，因為「我愛的是他這個人&hellip;」，令賓客都好感動。她明確表示：「不愛黃金只愛你。」<br />\n<br />\n賓客：「兩人很合襯！」<br />\n不過，女方父母就好像對男方不是太滿意，又話「我們只希望女兒過得幸福，只要這個男人對我們女兒好，我們就放心的把女兒嫁給他，男人最重要的不是相貌和外貌。」現場賓客透露，新娘家景本身唔錯，所以兩人很合襯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3305735_14670409355b0673daeb17b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F3305735_14670409355b0673daeb17b.jpg&h=6d5ad4d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3305738_2571057095b0673f5455d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F3305738_2571057095b0673f5455d1.jpg&h=6c47a3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3305739_10994884825b0673fe6df5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F3305739_10994884825b0673fe6df5f.jpg&h=f1412915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3305742_5989067675b067409a13e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F3305742_5989067675b067409a13e9.jpg&h=f8916662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47247b803ea71ff1a311366dd74d3cf48b28234a","tid":684204,"uid":65743,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/185551_5915d87dc71b136ceffbbcb66a4195db.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F185551_5915d87dc71b136ceffbbcb66a4195db.gif&h=54bb369a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6b356c64584f845f55caadd378c68ffb8647ae4","tid":684204,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"掛哂金話唔愛黃金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303b61907c5e8650b60a076224e4a266c747f6ba","tid":684204,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b356c64584f845f55caadd378c68ffb8647ae4","tid":684204,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"掛哂金話唔愛黃金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔講都還好<br />\n一講成浸虛偽味出哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb35f959f00dc349dffb32315deee13e492dc2b","tid":684204,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f9745361ae2fda2c929b12b7b3061c37d7b3d13","tid":684204,"uid":13897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"你話哩d叫真愛我實信架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74901cfdbe7ccc7baf0964e9ac42f2b81153f2cb","tid":684204,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:06:10.000Z","msg":"個女人換過個鼻黎？"},{"pid":"9e50f9fa8ab46a7d0679